	Array
	
	WAP to accept two integer and find their sum using arrays.
	
	Category 1: No arguments and no return value (sum)
	Category 2: Accepts arguments with not return value (fibonacci)
	Category 3: Arguments and return a value (Area)
	Category 4: No argument but returns a value
	Category 5: Return multiple values
	
	HW - Cite 2-2 examples of each of the above categories of function.
	
